{"tid":2237075,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"央視指NBA持續釋出善意決定明復播 一度因莫利撐港暫停","createTime":"2020-10-10T03:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T03:56:10.000Z","uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"971a0e777d67483eb2851af24c6ae9dc8c1fd6eb","tid":2237075,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T03:43:34.000Z","msg":"中央廣播電視總台發言人周五（9日）指，周六（10日）上午恢復播出NBA比賽。<br />\n<br />\n發言人指，籃球運動在中國有廣泛群眾基礎和球迷的收視需求，央視體育頻道恢復播出NBA比賽是正常的轉播安排。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，在剛過去的中國10.1、中秋雙節，NBA祝福中國球迷；也注意到NBA持續表達善意，特別是年初以來，NBA為中國抗疫等方面做出「積極努力」。<br />\n<br />\nNBA早前向武漢捐贈超過1,000萬人民幣（下同）的醫療用品，包括一套價值200萬的醫療設備，用於對抗疫情；NBA總裁施華也有呼籲球員捐錢，有指此舉是希望與中國修復關係。<br />\n<br />\nNBA 侯斯頓火箭隊總經理莫利（Daryl Morey）去年10月在社交媒體發表支持香港反修例運動的言論，被中國指「發表不當言論」，央視隨後暫停轉播NBA賽事，多間內地企業亦暫停對NBA的贊助。有報道指，NBA本賽季因失去中國市場，導致收視率、贊助商及各方面收入損失約2億美元（約15.5億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201009/P272PSPPOVF3NDUCRYXI7IG6XE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1NibKVcyfrIUgoh7vvuFAY9mMjH9c8TpywewbahH42XV4cXlhxac4dUcU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201009%2FP272PSPPOVF3NDUCRYXI7IG6XE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1NibKVcyfrIUgoh7vvuFAY9mMjH9c8TpywewbahH42XV4cXlhxac4dUcU&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDPsf6ZhrNwlVLGl95Ukzwcs%3D&h=318c47f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201009%2FP272PSPPOVF3NDUCRYXI7IG6XE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1NibKVcyfrIUgoh7vvuFAY9mMjH9c8TpywewbahH42XV4cXlhxac4dUcU&h=68ab102f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201009/P272PSPPOVF3NDUCRYXI7IG6XE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source